  "name": "Ki Wall (Sage)",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whenever the sage would be struck by an attack, he may spend a ki point as an immediate action to create a protective barrier of ki, granting him a deflection bonus to his AC equal to twice the number of chi gong dice he possesses against that attack. The sage may also use this ability whenever he would need to make a Reflex saving throw against a spell or effect to add a bonus equal to the number of chi gong dice he possesses to his roll.</p>\n",
